    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You unleash a radiant fire that burns away the taint of undeath. Make a spell attack roll against the target's AC, dealing 2d6 fire damage and 1d4 persistent fire damage on a hit. If the target is undead, all fire damage becomes vitality if it would be more detrimental. On a critical hit, double the initial damage, but not the persistent damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1) </strong>The initial damage increases by 2d6, and the persistent damage increases by 1.</p><p>@Damage[(1d4+@item.rank)[persistent,fire]]{Scaling Persistent Fire Damage}</p><p>@Damage[(1d4+@item.rank)[persistent,vitality]]{Scaling Persistent Vitality Damage}</p>"
